[% META title = 'HelpDesk System' %]
[% META description = 'How to use and administer the HelpDesk support ticket system' %]
[% META roles = 'admin developer editor' %]

<h1>HelpDesk System</h1>
<p><em>Last updated: April 28, 2026</em></p>

<h2>Overview</h2>
<p>
The HelpDesk provides a support ticketing system for all Comserv-hosted sites.
Visitors and registered users submit support tickets through the HelpDesk interface.
Staff review and respond through the admin panel, and the system manages the full lifecycle
from submission through resolution and auto-closure.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>Table of Contents</h2>
<ol>
    <li><a href="#submitting">Submitting a Ticket (User)</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ticket-lifecycle">Ticket Lifecycle</a></li>
    <li><a href="#admin-views">Admin Ticket Views</a></li>
    <li><a href="#status-management">Status Management</a></li>
    <li><a href="#reminders">Sending Reminders</a></li>
    <li><a href="#auto-close">Auto-Close of Stale Tickets</a></li>
